'''Frog spawn''' is a [[food]] item that heals 250life points when eaten. Eating it yields the message: "You eat the frogspawn. Yuck." They can be used to feed a player's pet cat and are also used in [[crafting potion]]s in combination with a [[clean wergali]] at level 42 [[Herblore]]. Frog spawn is required for the [[Contract Claws]] mystery.

The easiest way to obtain frog spawn is to use the "Net" option on fishing spots in the south-western [[Lumbridge Swamp Caves]] area. A light source will be needed in order to fish. [[Fury shark outfit]]'s extra catch and consume functions work on frog spawn.

Players may also obtain frog spawn by catching a [[gourmet impling]] or looting a [[gourmet impling jar]]. This impling may be in the wild or in the [[Impetuous Impulses]] minigame. Frog spawn may also be a drop from a [[frog]] in the [[jade vine maze]].

Frog spawn cannot be noted.

