A '''tarromin potion (unf)''' is an unfinished potion made via the [[Herblore]] skill. Players make it by using a [[clean tarromin]] on a [[vial of water]].

It is used to make the [[Magic potion]] at level 5 by adding a [[Bead]], earning 35 xp. It can also be used to make the [[Strength potion]] at level 7 by adding a [[limpwurt root]], earning 40 [[experience]]. It is also used to make the [[Serum 207]] at level 15 by adding [[ashes]], earning 50 experience. In addition, it can also be used to make the [[Shrink-me-quick]] at level 52 by adding a [[Shrunk Ogleroot]], earning 6 experience.

