The '''extreme prayer potion'''  is an upgraded [[super prayer]] potion. It is made by combining three-dose super prayer potion with [[primal extract]] and [[spark chitin]] at level 117 [[Herblore]].

They restore [[Prayer]] points at 70 + 50% of the player's maximum Prayer points, or between 75 and 565 points depending on the player's Prayer level. This potion stacks with the [[holy wrench]] (+20 Prayer points) and [[reverence]] [[aura]] (and its upgrades). The reverence aura's bonus is added first (+3% for regular, +5% for greater, +7% for master, and +10% for supreme, respectively) and then the holy wrench bonus (+19 Prayer points) is added. This results in a total of {{#expr:floor((70+(990*0.5))*1.1+19)}} Prayer points gained per dose if the holy wrench as well as the [[supreme reverence aura]] are used.{{CiteReddit|url=https://www.reddit.com/r/runescape/comments/e93atl/have_extreme_prayer_potions_affected_by_holy/fagix30/|author=Mod Breezy|title=Have Extreme Prayer potions affected by Holy Wrench's prayer point boost, to make it more worth using Blessed Flask.|date=11 December 2019|quote=I took a quick look in to this just now since i did the original QA for the Extreme Prayer. As far as i can see it still works with the Holy Wrench, and it also works with Reverence aura. Both Rev aura and Holy Wrench also stack. At level 99 prayer the Extreme Prayer pot heals 565 points, with the Wrench it heals 584 points. At level 50 prayer it's 320 points without, and 330 points with. No reverence aura used here btw. As an FYI though, Reverence aura does 10% of the original heal then adds the Holy Wrench bonus.|archiveurl=http://archive.md/FNQmC|archivedate=18 December 2019}} 

Extreme prayers are the only potions that can fill the [[blessed flask]]; otherwise, [[super restore]] are much cheaper and easier to obtain with very minimal difference, as most content does not usually last long enough to justify using super or extreme prayer potions. Any dose of extreme prayer can be used to fill up a blessed flask, and five 4-dose extreme prayer potions are required in the making of said flask.

They can be made with the help of boosts, such as [[Advanced pulse core|pulse cores]] (minimum level 110), and the [[Assist System]] can be used to create the potion at a lower level.

This potion can be made into an [[extreme prayer flask]] by using at least six doses of it with a [[potion flask]]. Players do not need a specific level to turn potions into flasks.

