An '''adrenaline crystal''' is a reward obtained as noted drops from the [[Wilderness shared loot table]] or created at level 93 [[Herblore]] from [[inert adrenaline crystal]]s. The effects of the [[portable well]], [[Modified botanist's mask]], and [[scroll of cleansing]] work when making adrenaline crystals.

The crystal can be added to a three-dose [[adrenaline potion]] or a six-dose [[replenishment potion]] to upgrade them to a [[super adrenaline potion]] or [[enhanced replenishment potion]], respectively. Upgrading an adrenaline potion requires level 87 Herblore and grants 200 Herblore experience, and upgrading a replenishment potion requires level 90 Herblore and grants 256.9 Herblore experience.

The upgraded potions grant 30% adrenaline instead of 25% when consumed (replenishment still provides the normal [[super restore]] effect).

