A '''juju mining potion''' is a reward from the [[Herblore Habitat]] activity and from attaining level 99 in all skills. It requires level 74 [[Herblore]] to make (as well as level 80 [[Farming]] and level 80 [[Hunter]]). Making this potion grants 168 Herblore experience and requires a [[clean samaden]] and a [[draconic vine]].

Each dose of potion lasts for six minutes. When a dose is consumed, each ore-receiving swing has a 10% chance to gain a [[bottled stone spirit]] of the type of ore mined. This means that while using a juju mining potion the player generates 10% more ore per hour if they do not already have a stack of stone spirits. This only applies to ore rocks.

[[Perfect juju mining potion]]s can be made via the addition of [[harmony moss]] to a 3-dose vial of juju mining potion. Each dose of the perfect juju mining potion lasts one hour. In addition, whenever a stone spirit is consumed to generate an additional ore, the player's stamina bar immediately refills. This only works with standard ores and does not work with granite or sandstone rocks. 
