* {{UL|type=patch|update=Patch Notes (21 January 2019)|date=21 January 2019}}
** The description of juju mining potion and [[perfect juju mining potion]] reflected an outdated design, and they have been updated to correctly match their current effect.

* {{UL|type=patch|update=Patch Notes (7 January 2019)|date=7 January 2019}}
** Juju mining potions now have a chance to give free [[stone spirits]] when mining. (Stone spirits double ore yield.) [[Perfect juju mining potion]]s make mining faster when using stone spirits.
*** Prior to this, the effect of a juju mining potion was a 10% chance to summon a [[Stone spirit (juju mining)|stone spirit]] which would automatically bank your ores for 30 seconds, a chance to find an additional ore, and 10% bonus experience.

* {{UL|type=patch|update=Patch Notes (4 December 2017)|date=4 December 2017}}
