}}

==Trivia==
* When [[Divination]] was released, on [[20 August]] [[2013]], the effect of a juju mining potion was changed from banking the ores to giving additional experience and automatically smelting mined ores, due to the Divination item [[Signs of the Porter]] having the same effect as the old potion. This was reverted back to its original effect on [[10 November]] [[2014]] with the release of the second batch of Prifddinas, and the smelting effect was added to the perfect juju mining potion instead. Both potions retained the +10% XP boost however.

