A '''perfect juju mining potion''' is a potion made using the [[Herblore]] skill. It is made by combining a [[juju mining potion (3)]] with [[harmony moss]], requiring 80 Herblore and giving 126 experience. This makes a three dose potion, which can then be [[decanting|decanted]] into other doses by talking to [[Bob Barter (herbs)]]. It can also be turned into a six-dose [[Perfect juju mining flask]] by talking to [[Teplin Macagan]] with a [[potion flask]].

Each dose of the potion lasts for one hour. While the potion is in effect, each ore-receiving swing gives a 10% chance to gain a [[bottled stone spirit]] of the type of ore mined (this only works with ore rocks and concentrated deposits). In addition, whenever a stone spirit is consumed to generate an additional ore, the player's stamina bar immediately refills. This only works with standard ores and does not work with [[granite rock]]s, [[sandstone rock]]s, or [[crablet]]s.

