[[File:Ancient gravel detail.png|left|100px]]
'''Ancient gravel''' is a type of [[soil]] that is found while excavating at the [[Kharid-et Dig Site]], which requires at least level 5 [[Archaeology]], or at [[Senntisten Dig Site]], which is available from level 60.

It can be screened with level 5 Archaeology at the [[screening station]] at the [[Archaeology Campus]] to obtain [[Materials (Archaeology)|materials]] and rarely [[artefact]]s from the soil. Alternatively, the soil may be screened with the [[Sift Soil]] spell in the [[Lunar Spellbook]].

Screening ancient gravel yields 1 Archaeology [[experience]] each from level 5 to 37, which increases to 3 experience each from level 38 to 70, 5 experience each from level 71 to 92, 12 experience each from level 93 to 110  and 20 experience each from level 111 to 120. 

