The '''archaeology potion''' is a [[potion]] that boosts [[Archaeology]] by +3 levels when consumed. The levels will reduce at 1 per minute. It can be made at level 78 [[Herblore]], after learning the [[Archaeology potion recipe|recipe]], by combining an [[avantoe potion (unf)|unfinished avantoe potion]] with five of any type of [[soil]].

The [[archaeology potion recipe]] is tradeable and may be bought from the [[Grand Exchange]] for {{NoCoins|{{GEP|Archaeology potion recipe}}|c}}. Level 90 Archaeology is required to excavate from hotspots where recipe fragments can be obtained.

